        <updateDate>2020-06-19T14:33:41Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Securing America's Clean Fuels Infrastructure</b></p> <p>This bill extends the tax credit for alternative fuel vehicle refueling property through 2028. It also increases the allowable amount of such credit from $30,000 to $200,000 for any single item of refueling property.</p>]]></text>
